BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:4LijQrC-rQkxxxkIUBZCm
SUMMARY:Pilates for Core & Balance
DTSTAMP:20260326T121101Z
DTSTART:20260330T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Just under an hour of strength and balance training for standin
	g and in-motion stability. This is a Pilates-based approach to strengtheni
	ng\\\, stabilizing and building proprioceptive awareness for the core and 
